            "stanza_text": "Sur notre front, clair et beau,\nToujours brilla le flambeau\nQui dissipe les ténèbres.\nLe savetier Gavarni\nFit notre soulier verni.\nDonc, ne soyons pas funèbres !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Pour amuser nos destins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Nous avons les doux satins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "L'or tramé, la pourpre insigne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "C'est chez nous qu'Ève aux beaux yeux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "S'en délecte et sait le mieux",
