                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour amuser nos destins\nNous avons les doux satins,\nL'or tramé, la pourpre insigne.\nC'est chez nous qu'Ève aux beaux yeux\nS'en délecte et sait le mieux\nPorter ces feuilles de vigne."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "O toi, dont le petit nez",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "A des reflets satinés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Sous le zéphyr qui le fripe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et qui baise tes appas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Femme, ne te laisse pas",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
