                    "line_text": "Qui toujours le mets dedans,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Rafraîchis tes blanches dents",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Sur la mousse du champagne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L'homme, qui s'est nommé roi,\nGarde le pouvoir ; mais toi,\nSa dédaigneuse compagne,\nQui toujours le mets dedans,\nRafraîchis tes blanches dents\nSur la mousse du champagne."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Les théâtres, — je les plains,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Ne sont pas tout à fait pleins.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "A la meilleure des villes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Nous permettrons ce défaut ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Et nous saurons, s'il le faut,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Nous passer de vaudevilles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les théâtres, — je les plains,\nNe sont pas tout à fait pleins.\nA la meilleure des villes\nNous permettrons ce défaut ;\nEt nous saurons, s'il le faut,\nNous passer de vaudevilles."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Tentons-le, c'est un essai.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Et tout en plaignant Sarcey,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Dont le cher cœur en soupire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Devant les rubis du feu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Près d'une amante à l'œil bleu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "On pourra lire Shakspere.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tentons-le, c'est un essai.\nEt tout en plaignant Sarcey,\nDont le cher cœur en soupire,\nDevant les rubis du feu,\nPrès d'une amante à l'œil bleu,\nOn pourra lire Shakspere."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Le meilleur régal qu'on sert",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "N'est pas au café-concert.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Ce sont les douces diphthongues",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Et les mots imitatifs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Que les amoureux furtifs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Disent sur les chaises longues.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le meilleur régal qu'on sert\nN'est pas au café-concert.\nCe sont les douces diphthongues\nEt les mots imitatifs\nQue les amoureux furtifs\nDisent sur les chaises longues."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Que Gluck et Cimarosa",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Fassent taire Influenza !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
