                    "line_text": "Tant que sur un sein de lys",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Fleurit un bouton de rose.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que Gluck et Cimarosa\nFassent taire Influenza !\nCar c'est une douce chose\nDe chanter Amaryllis,\nTant que sur un sein de lys\nFleurit un bouton de rose."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Nous cherchions le trésor ; mais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Nous savons tout, désormais.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "La Science, triste sphinge,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "En son babil indiscret",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Nous a dit le grand secret :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Nous descendons tous du Singe.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous cherchions le trésor ; mais\nNous savons tout, désormais.\nLa Science, triste sphinge,\nEn son babil indiscret\nNous a dit le grand secret :\nNous descendons tous du Singe."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Nos aïeux, contents de peu,",
